OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry this
OL,6,Fevening with some late sunshine in
OL,7,Fmost places. Then staying dry
OL,8,Fovernight but cloud will spread inland
OL,9,Ffrom the east. Skye and Lochaber
OL,10,Fstaying mostly clear. Patchy frost.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA dry day. Overnight cloud
OL,13,Fwill gradually lift and break to allow
OL,14,Fperiods of afternoon sunshine. Best of
OL,15,Fthe sunshine across Skye and Lochaber.
OL,16,FWarm in the southwest.
OL,17,
OL,18,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,19,FStaying dry with plenty of sunshine
OL,20,Fonce any overnight cloud has cleared.
OL,21,FWarm in the sunshine. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
